Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁眼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的休息日  再睡个回笼觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.37,0:00:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  起床吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得洗点衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:52.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}摩擦…摩擦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5月9日 \N 『哗啦哗啦哗啦啦！！』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小宫  起床了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！由乃亲  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在院子里有个奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像…像是一大块东西在蠕动着…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院子里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听  发出奇怪的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那不是寻学姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.58,0:02:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻…寻学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是睡糊涂了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  啊  打哈欠？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.09,0:03:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻学姐  你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天气不是很好吗  所以我就想洗下窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.55,0:03:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想用仓库里的盆子在院子里洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就走到外面来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在想盆子大小不够怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  充气游泳池还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}咔嚓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:36.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}翻箱倒柜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是要洗窗帘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:04:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  因为盆子的大小不够用嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就没想过在浴池里洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以打扰一下沙英的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐们在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  乃莉  小荠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在洗窗帘  乃莉你们要不要也一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗窗帘？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的窗帘买来还没多久  没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗帘最近才买
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:45.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}カーテン最近買うてん，谐音冷笑话，说的是关西方言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道说得不是很好啦  而且在这边人家也听不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好厉害  水变成黑色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我还以为我保养得很干净了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是灰尘之类的吧  真是吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.34,0:05:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说因为是日积月累的变化而没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是这样一点一点地变得如此污秽的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小荠这样淡淡地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来觉得很意味深长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐寻学姐  我可以和小宫一起踩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做红酒时的踩葡萄就是这种感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}赞岐乌冬面的面团是脚踩制作。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑中浮现出了乌冬面面团的制作画面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐她们感情可真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还没有吃早餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随意去烘些面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:06:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去煎荷包蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鸡蛋够不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那还有4个  拿去煎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把所有人的份一起煎了  现在看上去好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火腿是小荠提供的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是豪华的早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  小宫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:37.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大口咬下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  忍不住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溏心蛋很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  蛋黄好像要流出来似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃煎得不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我放洗涤剂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小宫好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想起个好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿吸管和纸杯来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去像真的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家在玩吹泡泡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在洗房间里的窗帘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看上去很干净
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上却很脏  吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师的衣服好像也有洗的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是脏了的话我们来洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是纯白无暇的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老师接下来要出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件连衣裙很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要陪朋友去试穿婚纱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我约了时间  就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我试穿了可爱婚纱的话  就发照片给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要试穿吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是要去试穿吉野屋老师自己的婚纱吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  有什么不好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然好像已经过了适婚年龄了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗涤完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿去…啊  好重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸满水后就变得这么重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这么重的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽全力绞一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  寻学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那……那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  小荠  发出这么大的声音真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  能不能暂时先把窗帘放进房里去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早的天气预报说到过…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是窗帘已经泡湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  又不是小荠的错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么大的东西没法晾在房间里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许还是可以的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  在哪里？  要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…在晾干吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能晾得干吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  才一下子就湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然淋浴  可以用来洗头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  不快点去换衣服的话会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么由乃亲回见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雨变得黏黏的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:11:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不就这样去洗个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好清爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能冲走看不见的污渍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:28.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5月9日  完  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:28.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}待续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师  今天的课程都结束了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的老师全都去教室里开班会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生们一定都等得脖子长了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就去教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  吃了午饭就犯困了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完就睡会变成牛的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桑原老师好过分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校长  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野屋老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛什么的太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还什么都没有说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我才不是牛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立  敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这不听话的身体我不想多说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？是指牛奶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都没有说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}　\N5\N月\N2\N5\N日\N
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(770,400)}『\N欢\N迎\N来\N到\N烤\N肉\N乐\N园\N！\N』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是吉野屋老师就那样走掉了再也没回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  马上就被校长拎回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底在搞些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部到齐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是房东啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.89,0:13:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说我们等下去吃烤肉自助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东好像会请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种表情是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃莉和小荠搬过来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.52,0:14:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受房东之托  大家一起打扫了103和203
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦地板和打扫厨房之类的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天的打扫很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  那时候作为回礼买了便当给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说她要请吃烤肉自助的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得有点受打击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:26.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月的临时的打工比预想外的顺利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想偶尔来个特别招待啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高兴点吧  这可是自助哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.90,0:14:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是烤肉  寿司和蛋糕都能随便吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宫  你不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全不知道店里的人能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间限制为100分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盘子里如果有剩的会加钱  注意不要拿太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.02,0:15:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家去拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  要从哪里开始呢  好犹豫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？怎…怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都喝什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了可尔必思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是可乐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不能喝  第一杯看情面也要来杯啤酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在对未成年人说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.93,0:15:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  开玩笑啦  沙英你太较真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始果然开始想吃烤舌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特地拿了很多  大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舌是指牛的舌头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  由乃是第一次吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  因为烤肉一直都是在家里吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:17.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛的舌头还真是薄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃  不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五花肉和里脊肉都超好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我完全不知道五花肉和里脊肉是哪一部分的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得里脊肉是在头的这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五花肉是在肋骨的附近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然烤肉就是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉自助还真是天国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:17:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  因为房东几乎不吃肉以外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得有点浪费呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.80,0:17:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费的可是你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司  寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:15.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}请自由使用芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还能继续吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖阳庄特别节目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司轮盘赌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮盘赌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面有一块寿司被我放了足量的芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃中的人要被罚给暖阳庄和我家除草
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  暖阳庄就算了  连房东的家也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  我吃不了芥末啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吃太多鼻子会呛到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望不会吃中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说不玩这游戏不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们忘了吗？  今天可是我请客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司也很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我的也安全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  难道房东…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己设下的陷阱自己却中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  我运气是不是很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要记得来哦  暖阳庄的除草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这五种蛋糕我都想吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话能帮我吃一半吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:59.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是每一个都很小  自己吃不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但全部吃过之后  应该会再拿很多自己喜欢吃的那种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英学姐是不是被利用了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总共是21000円
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人3000円  六个人不是18000円吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东你的那份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一个人帮我出500吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里的人给了我口香糖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完烤肉就该抽烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟呢  烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.81,0:19:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东你不是在戒烟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  所以现在要加油忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要戒烟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们考试合格之前我都不抽烟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是假话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房东  今天多谢款待了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在回家好麻烦啊  谁能留宿我一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你要在暖阳庄里留宿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出拳  石头剪刀布…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.17,0:20:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对请客吃烤肉的人该有的回应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理得很干净嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  不要客气  放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不愿意嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是制服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很多年没穿过了  能穿得下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉闻上去好香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都没有洒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是女高中生的香味吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才有听到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.39,0:21:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来称个体重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  小宫你真有勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次称是上礼拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有没有增加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  重了3公斤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡出很多汗会不会体重就不加了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.71,0:21:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  脑袋充血了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望今天的营养能够让我长高
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能够长高
